Package com.example.baard.Controllers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlarmReceiver
    Implements the receiver to be called by an Alarm Manager to then instantiate a notification Made with reference to: https://developer.android.com/training/notify-user/build-notification.html#notify https://thenewboston.com/forum/topic.php?id=13015
    ElasticSearchController
    Implements communication tasks with the elastic search server http://cmput301.softwareprocess.es:8080/cmput301f17t02/
    ElasticSearchController.AddUserTask
    Class to control Async background task that will create a user in the database and return the User class.
    ElasticSearchController.DeleteUserTask
    Async Task to delete a user from the database
    ElasticSearchController.GetAllUsersTask
    Class to control Async background task that will grab all users from the database
    ElasticSearchController.GetUserTask
    Class to control Async background task that will grab a user from the database
    ElasticSearchController.UpdateUserTask
    Class to control Async background task that will update a user in the database
    ExpandableListAdapter
    Adapter for Expandable List Views in Daily Habits and All Habits Fragments of Main Activity Referenced and copied from https://www.androidhive.info/2013/07/android-expandable-list-view-tutorial/
    FileController
    Controls JSON Serialization and Elastic Searches for loading and saving users
    SerializableImage
    Serializes images
    TypefaceSpan
